---
title: Tuscan Pork & Roast Veggie Spaghetti with Garlic Pangrattato & Parmesan
description: 'Pangrattato' is Italian for breadcrumb and it provides a delicious, traditional crunch when sprinkled over pasta. In this dish, we've teamed the traditional tomato sauce with seasoned pork mince and roasted veggies for a meal that looks every bit as good as it tastes.
